<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2669903>
    dc:description "FIGURE 87. Holotype of Scyliorhinus torrei Howell-Rivero, 1936, MCZ 147, female, 250 mm TL (Havana, Cuba). A, ventral view; B, lateral view. Scale bar = 20 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2669903/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2669905>
    dc:description "FIGURE 88. Scyliorhinus torrei. A, CAS 65845, female, 255 mm TL (Cuba, 23°34’N, 79°07’W); B–F, USNM 157852, male, 285 mm TL (Cuba, 22°55’N, 79°27’W). A, B, ventral view of head; C, lateral view of head; D, lateral view of head; E, dorsal view of head; F, detail of pelvic fins and claspers. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2669905/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2669907>
    dc:description "FIGURE 89. Teeth of Scyliorhinus torrei; labial view, USNM 157852, male, 285 mm TL (Cuba, 22°55’N, 79°27’W). a, anterior tooth; c, commissural; l, lateral; ps, parassymphysial. Scale bar = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2669907/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2669909>
    dc:description "FIGURE 90. Dermal denticles of Scyliorhinus torrei. A–C, CAS 65845, female, 255 mm TL (Cuba, 23°34’N, 79°07’W); D–F, USNM 157852, male, 285 mm TL (Cuba, 22°55’N, 79°27’W). A, D, region above pectoral fin base; B, E, region below first dorsal fin origin; C, F, region below second dorsal fin insertion. Scale bar = 250 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2669909/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2669911>
    dc:description "FIGURE 91. Clasper of Scyliorhinus torrei; dorsal view, USNM 157852, 285 mm TL (Cuba, 22°55’N, 79°27’W). A, external morphology; B, skeleton. crh, cover rhipidion; end, endstyle; en, envelope; erh, exorhipidion; hp, hipopyle; rd, dorsal marginal cartilage; rv, ventral marginal cartilage; td, dorsal terminal cartilage; td2, dorsal terminal 2 cartilage; tdc, terminal dermal cover; tv, ventral terminal cartilage; tv2, ventral terminal 2 cartilage. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2669911/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2669913>
    dc:description "FIGURE 92. Map showing the geographic distribution of Scyliorhinus torrei based on the material examined in this study. Black star indicates the type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2669913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

